Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們不敢茍同\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:27.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為逃避官方追捕，我們秘密行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hunted by the authorities, we work in secret.{\r}
