Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但無論是受害者還是罪犯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but victim or perpetrator,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:34.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一旦你的號碼出現，我們就會找到你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}if your number's up, we'll find you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:28.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,紐約警局\N{\reng_1 - 1080}NYPD.{\r}
