Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:41.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What the hell are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,抓壞蛋\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Catching the bad guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,三輛警車馬上就到\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah. We had three RPM's coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你懂什麼叫支援嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know, a little thing called backup?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有時我們要等支援，不開槍\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know, sometimes we wait for it instead of shooting people,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:51.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,以免在曼哈頓市中心造成恐慌\N{\reng_1 - 1080}'causing mayhem in the middle of Manhattan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:52.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,今天可真是熱\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's hot as hell out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我得給大家節約點時間\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Figure I'd save us all some time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,聽著，你現在不是獨行俠了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Listen, you're not a lone wolf anymore, pal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是警察，得敬畏你的工作\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're a cop, and you need to start respecting the job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,帶警徽是要遵守規章制度的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}There are rules and regulations that come with that badge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說的好像你沒違反過一樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Like you haven't bent those rules before?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可我不再犯了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, well, I don't anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你知道還有誰遵守制度嗎？新隊長\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know who else doesn't? The new captain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,真是稀奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, that was novel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,眾目睽睽之下擊傷罪犯？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Shooting a perp in front of hundreds of witnesses?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,真有你的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Subtle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這傢伙可能餘生\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The guy's probably gonna need crutches{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,都要拄枴杖了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}for the rest of his life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這是你這個月第三還是第四次\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What is that, the third or fourth guy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.98,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,打傷人膝蓋了，萊利？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}you kneecapped this month, Riley?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,第四次，長官\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fourth, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,槍法那麼準\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I suppose I should give you points{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我都想表揚你了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}for being such a good shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:26.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們是去調查鮑曼謀殺案的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You were supposed to be working the Bowman homicide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這算怎麼回事？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What the hell were you doing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在市中心追鬧事癮君子？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}chasing a druggie smash and grabber in midtown?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們在追一條線索\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We were working a developmental.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,找死的線索嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Into what, an early grave?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.47,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,全市都有我們的線人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We got CI's all over town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:39.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那些線人幫你們結過案嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Those CI's help you close any cases yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,警務數據系統的數據很難看\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The CompStat numbers are an embarrassment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,上兩個月兇殺案上升了20％\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Homicides are up 20% in the last two months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我都想辭職了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm ready to fire me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事，先生們？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What's going on, gentlemen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,天氣很熱，隊長，火氣也大\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's a heat wave, Captain. Tempers flare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.48,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,城市狀況開始變差了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The city's taking a turn for the worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得更加努力\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We need to do a better job{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,事先解決這些狀況\N{\reng_1 - 1080}of getting out in front of this thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我要確認一下，你們是跟我合作還是跟我作對？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I need to know, are you guys working with me or against me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們只想履行職責，隊長\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We just want to do our job, Captain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊出去\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So get your asses out there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,幹點正事給我看看\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and show me what you can really do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是的，長官\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你，穿名貴西裝這位\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey, you in the fancy suit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你現在是隊裏的一員\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're part of a team now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不能再像緝毒警那樣亂來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No more narco cowboy nonsense,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還有，這幾天別給我亂開槍\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and try not to shoot anyone for a few days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You hear me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,清清楚楚\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Loud and clear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,既然聽到了，那就幹活吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You heard what she said. We got work to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,別緊張，萊諾\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Relax, Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,聽著，神奇先生\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Listen, Mr. Fabulous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我得付房屋貸款，贍養費\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I got a mortgage, alimony,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,過幾年孩子也要上大學了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and a kid going to college in a few years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看到這地方了？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You see this place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這是我的飯碗\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This is my livelihood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且充滿了官僚主義\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And it's filled with too much bureaucracy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,缺少實際行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and not enough direct action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這就是我的生活，警探\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This is my real life, Detective.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不是什麼超級英雄的掩護身份\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not some superhero cover identity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I hear you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,才怪\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不，我說真的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No, I'll work on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我花了二十年\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I've spent the past two decades{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一直在學如何不守規矩\N{\reng_1 - 1080}learning how not to color inside the lines.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能需要點時間去調整\N{\reng_1 - 1080}May take me a second or two to figure it out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,萊利警探，我們有新號碼了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Detective Riley, we have a new number.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不是時候，教授\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now's not the best time, Professor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我在工作\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm at work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,避開起疑心的上司\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Circumventing suspicious employers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也是我們的新挑戰之一，約翰\N{\reng_1 - 1080}is part of our new challenge, John.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,請盡快\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Please hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>上，大熊</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go get it, Bear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,上，快上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go get it. Go get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>抓住它，大熊</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go get 'em, Bear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>抓住它</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go get 'em.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,肖小姐，別這樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ms. Shaw, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,它不需要這種鼓勵\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He doesn't need any more encouragement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你不希望它找到？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Don't you want him to catch it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在新辦公室找死老鼠內臟？當然不希望\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not if it involves finding rat entrails in our new office, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大熊，<i>過來</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Bear, hier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,機器幫我們找到了新辦公室\N{\reng_1 - 1080}While the machine may have given us a place of operation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:02.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但它解決不了我們的經濟狀況\N{\reng_1 - 1080}it didn't account for our financial situation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,恐怕你的飯錢和房租要開始\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm afraid your meals and rent are going to have to start{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,從你的實際薪水裏扣了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}coming out of your actual paychecks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好在我現在打兩份工\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, it's a good thing I'm working two jobs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,化妝品櫃檯工資少得可憐\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The makeup counter pays like crap.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你知道一雙高檔高跟鞋有多貴嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And do you know how expensive a nice pair of heels are?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,簡直是搶錢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What a racket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,等我獲取到其他資金再說吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Until I access some auxiliary funds,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在我們別無選擇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we have no choice{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,只能將就現在身份的社會經濟狀況\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but commit to our identities' socioeconomic status.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Copy that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這個月就吃拉麵和兩塊錢的牛排吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ramen and two buck chuck for the rest of the month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得快點\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We'll need to make this fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我現在在新隊長和搭檔的黑名單上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm on the new captain's hit list and my partner's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,怎麼，你又開槍打人了？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What, did you shoot somebody else?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:38.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你得更小心點，約翰</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You have to be more careful, John.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:40.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,機器給我們設計的身份\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The identities that the machine created for us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,非常珍貴，應心存感激\N{\reng_1 - 1080}are precious commodities not to be taken for granted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,外面真熱\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It was hot out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不提了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Never mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說說新號碼吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's hear about that new number.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,安德烈·庫珀\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Andre Cooper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在布朗克斯區出生長大\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Born and raised in The Bronx.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:01.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,做過碼頭工，現在是專業社交顧問\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Former longshoreman turned professional social liaison.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,社交什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A social what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,專業約會顧問\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A professional wingman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,男人自己勾搭不到女人的時候\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He's the guy people hire{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就可以請他這種人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}when they can't pick up women on their own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為什麼要放棄工會工作\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Why leave a union gig{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>去教絕望男人搭訕技巧</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to teach desperate men pick-up tricks?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我建議去近距離看看庫珀怎麼幹的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I suggest we get close to Cooper's operation and find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是說偽裝成客戶？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You mean go undercover as a client?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不行，芬奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not it, Finch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,別擔心，裏斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, don't worry, Reese.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,哈羅德和我覺得\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Harold and I decided{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得找一個\N{\reng_1 - 1080}that we needed somebody{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,人際交往能力更強\N{\reng_1 - 1080}with a few more people skills{\r}
