Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,米奇是我在碼頭的老朋友\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mick is an old friend from the docks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,老相識了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We've known each other a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是啊，可不\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, I'd say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好久沒來這種地方了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Way before you'd ever come in a place like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.98,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是啊，你怎麼來這了？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So true. So what got you here?{\r}
