Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這位是誰？客戶嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who's this guy? Client?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這是萊諾\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This is Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,新客戶\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He's new.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是一個熟人介紹的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It was gift from a friend, uh, a guy I knew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,放鬆啦，酷哥\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey, don't worry, killer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,當初還是安德烈幫我約到我老婆的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Andre actually hooked me up with my wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他會是你見過最棒的把妹達人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He's the best pick-up artist you'll ever meet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你住在市中心區對吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey, you live in midtown, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,市區東邊？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Midtown East?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,對呀，沒錯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, that's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,約個時間一起吃飯吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We got to grab a meal sometime soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,見到你太棒了，夥計，回見\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's great seeing you, man. Take care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我看見了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I saw that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:50.16,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,嘿，小子\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey, pal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,勾搭我女朋友？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Checking out my girl?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我沒發現她名花有主\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know what? I didn't realize she was anyone's girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,怎麼…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What the--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,紐約警局，今晚你就別想好好過了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}NYPD. You're cut off for the rest of the night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,明白嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You understand me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who the hell are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你做完口供了？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You finish making your statement?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.47,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你有什麼要說的嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Do you have a statement,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:43.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,比如為什麼在工作方面對我撒謊？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}like why you lied to me about what you do for a living?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你在調查我嗎，萊諾？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Am I under investigation, Lionel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你犯了什麼事需要被調查嗎，安德烈？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Did you do something to warrant investigation, Andre?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:50.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不，當然沒有，你在迴避問題\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No, of course not. You're avoiding the question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是法斯克\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fusco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>等一下，萊諾</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hold up, Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我認為這個號碼可能是個罪犯</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I think our number might be a perp after all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你發現了什麼？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What'd you find?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,紅鉤區有件麥洛·雅各布斯謀殺案\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Open homicide in Red Hook on a man named Milo Jacobs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:07.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,被害人九個月前在碼頭當保安\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He worked security on the docks up until nine months ago,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,跟槍支失蹤是同一時期\N{\reng_1 - 1080}around the same time that gun shipment went missing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:12.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我這裏有麥洛和庫珀間的通話記錄\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And I have got phone calls here between Milo and Cooper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能是他們一起偷走了貨物\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Maybe they stole that shipment together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:24.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是我搭檔問我情況\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's my partner checking in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:27.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我說謊是因為警察不會雇約會顧問\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I lied because cops don't hire wingmen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:33.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那幫傢伙要是知道了，肯定要揍扁我的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The guys find out, they'll bust my chops to my grave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,今天還沒結束\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, the day's not done,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你朋友又提前付錢了，那麼…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and your friend paid in advance, so...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,什麼？你想繼續？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What? You want to keep going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:47.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是個英雄，我們該利用好這個名頭\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're a hero. We should capitalize on that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:50.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,咱們趕下一場\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I have another event we could catch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還能糟到哪去呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What's the worst that could happen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:04.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,裏面有主廚的口供\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The chef's confession is on there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你抓了溫迪·蒙哥馬利的丈夫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You got Wendy Montgomery's husband.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,幹得好啊，萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- Well done, Riley. - Hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,眼睛上的傷我就不過問了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I won't ask about the eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你搭檔在哪？我也想祝賀他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Where's your partner? I want to congratulate him too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,法斯克在追另一宗案子\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fusco's taking the lead on another case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,接下來呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What's next?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,汽車代理商中槍案\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That car dealership owner who got shot?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他挪用自己公司的錢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He was embezzling money from his own company.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:21.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你認為他的僱員與此事有關？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You think his employees were in on it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:23.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我認為他們找到了他藏錢的地方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I think they found out where he was hiding the money{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後殺了他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and killed him for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我查了他們的信用卡記錄\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I tapped into their credit reports.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>自從他們老闆死後</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They've been spending a lot of money{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:28.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們一直在大把花錢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}since their boss' death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是否需要知道\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Do I want to know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:32.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼搞到信用卡記錄的？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}how you got those credit reports?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,上午不順嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Bad morning?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,哦，我包裏現在還有煙味\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, my pocketbook still smells like cigarettes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,戒煙搞得我煩得要死\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Quitting has me edgy as hell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:42.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不過要麼用膏藥，要麼看醫師\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but it was either the patch or a hypnotherapist,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:44.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我才不信什麼空話大道理\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and I don't believe in that hippie nonsense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:47.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,或許我們能把你的煩躁轉化成優勢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Maybe we can use that edginess of yours to our advantage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有點意思\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm intrigued.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:51.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說來聽聽\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tell me more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我告訴過你不要再調查下去了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I told you no more developmentals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:00.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我正在調查一條線索…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I was working up a lead--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:01.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你的工作效率在下滑，萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Your numbers are down, Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果你結不了案\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If you don't start closing more cases,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:04.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我就把你調去看管證據倉庫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm gonna ship you off to evidence lockup{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:07.48,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,再找個能結案的人來干\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and find someone who can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是萊利警探\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm Detective Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們哪個先跟我談？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Which one of you wants to go first?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:27.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,鮑曼的案子我已經被審問過了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I've already been questioned about Mr. Bowman's murder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我那時一無所知，現在也一無所知\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Didn't know anything then. Don't know anything now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:32.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有謠言說鮑曼先生脾氣不太好\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I heard a rumor Mr. Bowman had a bit of a temper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:36.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還聽說他總是遷怒於你，你厭惡透了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I also heard you were sick of him taking it out on you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是啊，換成是你，也會煩透的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, well, you'd be sick of it too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:40.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,業績不好，他就衝我們大喊大叫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He'd scream at us if we didn't sell enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:43.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果我們沒努力改善也是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}or if we weren't pushing upgrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:46.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,又不是每個人都想要汽車霧燈\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, well, not everyone wants fog lights.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:48.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看見我那暴脾氣的長官了沒？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}My ballbuster of a captain out there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,她往死裏催我結這個案子\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She is all over me about closing up this case{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一定要在今天之前\N{\reng_1 - 1080}before the end of the day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我只是擔心我的飯碗</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm just worried about my job,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:58.46,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,所以咱們談個條件怎麼樣？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}so what do you say we make a deal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:01.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我不知道你什麼意思\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I don't know what you mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:03.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,- 我一無所知\N<i>- 得啦，連尼</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- I don't know anything. - Come on, Lenny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:05.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你倆找到了鮑曼藏錢的地方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You guys found out where Bowman was keeping the money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後殺了他，對嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and you killed him for it, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:08.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,- 不是這樣的\N- 當然是這樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- That's not true. - Sure, it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:11.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道你倆哪位\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What I don't know is which one of you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:14.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,想先跟我談條件\N{\reng_1 - 1080}wants to make a deal with me first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:18.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,什麼條件？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What kind of deal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:22.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們幫我結案，分我一半的錢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You help me close up this case, give me half the money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:26.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後就一筆勾銷\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and we'll make this all go away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:30.16,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們還可以確定讓連尼背黑鍋\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hell, we'll even make sure that Lenny takes the fall for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:32.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,因為反正巴裏會說都是你的主意\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Because Barry's gonna say it was all your idea anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:34.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他撒謊！這都是巴裏的主意！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He's a liar! This was all Barry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.73,0:24:36.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,分一半錢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Half?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:39.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一半\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Half.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:42.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，但一定算巴裏的責任，放過我，行不？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fine, but this all falls on Barry, not me, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這算結案了嗎，長官？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Does that work for you, Captain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.55,0:24:51.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看來你又結了個案子，萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Looks like you closed another case, Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:55.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,繼續努力吧，餐具大獎等你拿\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Keep it up, you'll get that set of steak knives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.36,0:25:04.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很久沒這麼開心了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The most fun I've had in a while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:05.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,- 演得不錯\N- 你也是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- Good game. - You too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:07.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很想慶祝一下\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Love to celebrate,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.20,0:25:10.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不過既然你正走運，這個重案就交給你了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but since you're on a roll, it's a priority homicide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:12.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,剛來自專員辦公室\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It just came in from the Commissioner's Office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.27,0:25:14.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,非法街頭小販撤回了口供\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Illegal street vendor recanted his statement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他被威脅了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The vendor's scared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.61,0:25:17.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你得比威脅他的人更厲害才行\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Be scarier than the guy who made him clam up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:19.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,遵命，長官\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.25,0:25:34.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看見沒，萊諾\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You see, Lionel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.02,0:25:35.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,目光接觸\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Eye contact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.59,0:25:37.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>對哦，萊諾</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.56,0:25:43.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,婦女慈善活動是遇到女士們的絕佳途徑\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Women's charities are a great way to meet ladies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.43,0:25:46.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,女士人數更多，還可以打著慈善的名頭\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're always outnumbered, and it's for a good cause.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.80,0:25:48.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不覺得有點狡猾嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Isn't that a little tacky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.24,0:25:49.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我更喜歡稱之為「戰略」\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I prefer the word "Strategic."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.77,0:25:53.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,別擺弄袖口了，靚仔\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Stop primping, gorgeous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.41,0:25:55.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有人在看你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Somebody's watching you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.71,0:25:59.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在拍賣會旁邊的女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Lady by the silent auction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.72,0:26:01.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,來點微笑\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Great smile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.82,0:26:03.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼辦？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What do we do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.45,0:26:04.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,她已經主動給你機會了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She's already doing all the work for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.75,0:26:08.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,快過去吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now off you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.40,0:26:16.00,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是否感覺有點緊張\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are you feeling a little exposed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:18.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,手持反坦克導彈\N{\reng_1 - 1080}having an anti-tank missile in our possession{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.27,0:26:20.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在曼哈頓中心，還是只有我在緊張？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}in the middle of Manhattan, or is it just me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.70,0:26:24.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,撒瑪利亞絕不會找一個帶著AT4的大學教授的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Samaritan won't be looking for a college professor with an AT4.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.34,0:26:25.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我擔心的不是撒瑪利亞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's not Samaritan I'm worried about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.94,0:26:27.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那是誰？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Then who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.11,0:26:28.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,國土安全局，紐約警局\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Homeland Security. NYPD.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.34,0:26:30.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,女巡警\N{\reng_1 - 1080}An errant meter maid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.95,0:26:32.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,埃格雷？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Egret?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:35.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你是？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And you are?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:38.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,「該死的達賴喇嘛」，我是傑瑞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The freakin' Dalai Lama. I'm Jerry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.85,0:26:40.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是被你們聯繫過的另一個傢伙派來的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The guy who was sent by the other guy you contacted{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.42,0:26:41.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他說你們要把貨出手？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}about the thing you wanted to sell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:43.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你有買家？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You have a buyer for us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.09,0:26:49.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我原以為埃格雷長得會更兇一點\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I thought Egret would be more, uh, badass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:26:52.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,畢竟你名聲在外啊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I mean, you got that rep, you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.63,0:26:56.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可你看起來沒那麼壯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You don't look so tough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:59.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那是因為我只有兩種狀態，傑瑞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's because I have only two modes, Jerry...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:03.98,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,冷靜和憤怒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}calm and furious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.98,0:27:06.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很少有人能看到後者\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's a rare person that sees the latter{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.18,0:27:08.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還能活著跟別人談起\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and lives to talk about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:11.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.12,0:27:12.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.65,0:27:14.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I gotcha.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.29,0:27:16.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大夥兒淡定嘛\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Everyone relax now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.16,0:27:18.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Follow me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.33,0:27:30.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我也喜歡</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I-I like it too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.50,0:27:32.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我不懂這是個什麼，但是我喜歡\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I don't know what it is, but I like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:35.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,得了，法斯克\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, come on, Fusco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.17,0:27:37.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,直接問她要電話號碼吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Just ask her for her number already.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.41,0:27:40.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們還得搞清楚你的新朋友是不是罪犯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We need to figure out if your new buddy's a killer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.09,0:27:48.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>等一下</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Wait a sec.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.99,0:27:51.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>這人是誰？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who's this guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:57.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,碼頭工\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Longshoreman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.43,0:28:01.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,法斯克，帶上安德烈，快從後門離開\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fusco, grab Andre and go out the back exit now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.53,0:28:05.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，我得走了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I-- I'm sorry. I-I have to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.07,0:28:07.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛？為什麼不問她要電話號碼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What are you doing? Why didn't you get her number?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.04,0:28:08.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你有危險\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're in danger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.57,0:28:10.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們要離開這，快點\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We need to get you out of here right now, come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.19,0:28:23.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.46,0:28:31.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,胃抽筋真要命\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, wicked stomach cramps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.38,0:28:54.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,退後！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Back up!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:55.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,米奇，你不清楚你在幹什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mick, you don't know what you're doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.92,0:28:58.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,恐怕恰恰相反，夥計\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm afraid you got that the other way around, pal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.46,0:29:03.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,帶他上車，兩個都帶上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Get him in. Bring 'em both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.29,0:29:04.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們走\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.29,0:29:05.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們走，快！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's go, move!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.12,0:29:28.48,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我回到畫廊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know, I went back to the art gallery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.49,0:29:30.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那個假安保也跑了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That fake security guard, he high-tailed it out of there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.35,0:29:32.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們一定想從安德烈身上得到什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They must want something from Andre.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.29,0:29:33.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不然，他早就被殺了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Otherwise he'd already be dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.72,0:29:35.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:38.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,米奇和庫珀一定是一起偷了那批貨\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mickey and Cooper must have stolen that shipment together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.33,0:29:40.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我敢說有人出賣了對方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I bet someone double-crossed someone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.90,0:29:43.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得跟蹤米奇的貨車\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We need to track Mickey's van.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.64,0:29:51.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你現在是警察</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're a cop now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.17,0:29:53.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>可以全權進入區域警覺系統了？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Full access pass to domain awareness?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.41,0:29:57.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,多虧了「老大哥」，我們也能監視別人了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Thanks to Big Brother, we can be watching too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.09,0:30:07.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,根據時間段標記，在20分鐘之前\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This has been time-stamped 20 minutes ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.16,0:30:09.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們走\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.26,0:30:12.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我不能去，肖\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I can't, Shaw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.00,0:30:15.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,莫雷諾隊長交給我一樁重案\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Captain Moreno handed me a priority homicide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.06,0:30:16.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,萬一沒及時找到法斯克\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What do you think this is gonna be{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.33,0:30:17.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你覺得會有什麼後果？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}if we don't get to Fusco soon?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.50,0:30:19.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,她盯我盯得很緊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She's got me under a microscope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.04,0:30:20.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果她發現了我的真實身份\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If she figures out who I really am,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.77,0:30:23.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,撒瑪利亞也會，那我們都完了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Samaritan will too, and we'll all be dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.11,0:30:27.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我是萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.21,0:30:28.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,遵命，長官\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:31.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我正在去調查小販的路上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm on my way to interview the vendor now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.35,0:30:35.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,呃，這人有點難找，長官…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, he's been a little bit hard to find, ma'am--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.02,0:30:38.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，不過我要帶上狗\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fine, but I'm taking the dog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.36,0:30:47.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你想告訴我你讓我攤上什麼事了嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You want to tell me what you got me involved in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.13,0:30:49.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,抱歉，萊諾\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm sorry, Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.86,0:30:52.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我本以為米奇不會再出現了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I thought Mickey was out of my life for good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.73,0:30:55.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們這群傢伙幹了什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What did you ass clowns do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.30,0:30:56.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我沒有\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.74,0:30:58.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是米奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mickey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.04,0:31:00.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有個叫多米尼克的商人給他錢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Some dealer named Dominic paid him off{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.61,0:31:02.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,讓他偷走一集裝箱的槍\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to disappear a container full of guns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.88,0:31:05.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他只是從系統中刪除了集裝箱\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He just deleted it out of the system.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.05,0:31:07.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,地方檢察官懷疑米奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}DA suspects Mickey's involved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.05,0:31:08.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們想讓我作證，我不肯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They want me to testify. I said I wouldn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.78,0:31:10.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}How come?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.89,0:31:17.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你知道為了正義而背棄朋友\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know how hard it is to turn your back on your friends{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:21.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有多難嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}because it's the right thing to do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:23.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.13,0:31:26.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我也算經歷過\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I know a little bit about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:29.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那你就能明白我為什麼沒招\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Then you understand why I didn't say anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.90,0:31:33.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說什麼悄悄話吶？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What are you girls gossiping about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:35.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,安德烈正跟我說你有多蠢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Andre here was just telling me what a moron you are{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.91,0:31:37.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,居然綁架警察\N{\reng_1 - 1080}for kidnapping a cop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.08,0:31:38.48,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>確實有點意外</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, that came as a bit of a surprise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.48,0:31:40.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,什麼時候跟條子混一起了，安德烈？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Since when are you hanging out with cops, Dre?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.68,0:31:43.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,萊諾是我的客戶，他是好人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Lionel's a client, and he's a good man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.62,0:31:44.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>放了他</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let him go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.92,0:31:46.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,太晚了，兄弟\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's too late for that, buddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.59,0:31:48.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,快說，我干零活這事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now just tell me what you've been saying to the DA{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.99,0:31:50.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你跟地檢官說了什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}about my little side job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.16,0:31:51.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,都說了我什麼也沒說\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I already told you. Nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.92,0:31:53.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我也希望如此\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I want to believe that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.33,0:31:55.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們認識15年了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You've known me for 15 years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.26,0:31:57.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你就像我兄弟，你知道我說的是實話\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're like a brother. You know I'm telling the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.03,0:31:59.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你曾經是我兄弟，但你拋棄了我\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You were my brother, but you abandoned me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.77,0:32:01.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,因為你愈發貪婪\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Because you got greedy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.27,0:32:04.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你身居正位，卻幹了不法勾當\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You took an honest job and you turned it dirty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:05.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我只是談生意\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I made a business deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.37,0:32:08.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是啊，跟幫派罪犯談生意\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yeah, with a criminal street gang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.34,0:32:10.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在還要讓好人幹壞事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now you got good men doing bad things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.81,0:32:12.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好人總會幹壞事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Good men do bad things all the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.65,0:32:14.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不，你比那些奸商還差勁\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No, you're worse than those dealers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.78,0:32:17.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,因為你對朋友下手，比如麥洛\N{\reng_1 - 1080}'cause you turned on your friends, like Milo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.45,0:32:19.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我也是迫不得已\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I did what I had to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.89,0:32:21.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果你殺了警察\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Look, if you kill a cop,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.89,0:32:24.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,政府就會通緝你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}the feds are gonna come looking for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.32,0:32:26.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不會\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.36,0:32:28.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們會通緝你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They're gonna come looking for you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.73,0:32:30.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,因為我會佈置成這樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}'cause that is how I'm gonna set it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.43,0:32:36.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,動手吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Get 'em ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.90,0:32:43.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒看見，我告訴他們…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I saw nothing. I told them--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.07,0:32:45.14,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,被害人死亡當晚你就在紅鉤區\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You were in Red Hook the night the victim died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:46.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們追蹤了你的手機\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We traced your cell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.74,0:32:49.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我沒在那\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I wasn't even there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.65,0:32:51.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我沒說謊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm not lying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.38,0:32:54.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那我幫你好好想想？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What if I help your memory?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.22,0:32:57.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是這樣的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Here's how this works.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:32:59.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要是你想起有用的事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You remember something useful,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.42,0:33:02.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我就給你這個信封\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and I give you this envelope{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.83,0:33:05.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,買你一個手袋\N{\reng_1 - 1080}in exchange for one of these lovely handbags.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.73,0:33:08.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,手袋是正品，對吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}These are genuine, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:12.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,把這錢包賣我\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Sell me this purse,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:14.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你就能展開新生活\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and you get to start a new life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.61,0:33:19.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但首先你得告訴我你看見了什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But first you need to tell me what you saw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.41,0:33:25.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你確定我們能信任這些先生？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're certain we can trust these gentlemen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.72,0:33:27.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,信任他們？當然不能\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Trust 'em? Of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.38,0:33:28.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不能信任任何人，埃格雷\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You can't trust anyone, Egret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:31.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你的世界不是這樣麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What world do you live in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.55,0:33:34.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這下有意思了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This is gonna be interesting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:36.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要是我們死了可就沒意思了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's going to be a lot less interesting once we're dead,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:38.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,葛洛弗女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ms. Groves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.04,0:33:52.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大熊，我數到三\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay, Bear, on three.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.31,0:33:55.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一，二…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}One, two...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.66,0:34:11.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>調查，</i> 大熊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Zoek, Bear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.93,0:34:14.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>調查</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Zoek.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.68,0:34:30.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我雇了朋友，確保這集裝箱\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I hired a friend to make sure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.41,0:34:32.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,絕不會到達目的地\N{\reng_1 - 1080}this container never reaches its destination.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.01,0:34:33.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,別擔心\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Don't worry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.61,0:34:36.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們很可能淹水之前就中暑死了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You'll probably die of heat stroke before you drown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.79,0:34:42.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們走\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.81,0:34:58.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,鼎鼎大名的埃格雷先生\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The famous Mr. Egret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:35:02.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你彷彿是憑空出現\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It seems you materialized out of nowhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.29,0:35:05.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後就無所不在了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now you are everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.92,0:35:07.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,怎麼做到的？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}How is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.83,0:35:10.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我非常注重隱私\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm a very private person.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.90,0:35:17.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:19.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我也一樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I am as well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.64,0:35:21.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們很幸運能找到我朋友，傑瑞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're lucky you know my friend, Jerry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:25.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們不信任外人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We don't trust outsiders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.32,0:35:40.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,15萬\N{\reng_1 - 1080}150,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.16,0:35:41.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你要數嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Would you like to count it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.99,0:35:44.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我和埃格雷先生都相信錢夠數\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mr. Egret and I are certain the money's all there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.43,0:35:48.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不，我不能這麼做\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No, I can't do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.93,0:35:50.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,- 哈羅德…\N- 對不起\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- Harold-- - I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.27,0:35:53.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這導彈不賣了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This missile is no longer for sale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.44,0:35:57.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我還以為你是說話算話的人，埃格雷先生\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I thought you were a man of your word, Mr. Egret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.27,0:36:00.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,賣導彈給犯罪團伙就另當別論\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not if it involves selling a rocket launcher to the mob.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.88,0:36:03.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,任何罪犯都不行\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Any mob.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.01,0:36:06.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這是我的底線\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That happens to be a line I'm not willing to cross.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.85,0:36:10.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,它太瞭解你了，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She knows you so well, Harold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.32,0:36:13.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在我們就能一石二鳥了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now we get to kill two birds with one stone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.13,0:36:22.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要不要把他們綁起來以防萬一？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Should we tie 'em up just in case?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.13,0:36:28.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,做這些事意義何在，葛洛弗女士？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What was the point of all this, Ms. Groves?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.20,0:36:31.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,做這麼荒唐的事能幫助什麼人？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}How did this ridiculous journey help anyone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.24,0:36:34.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,讓我給你看\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let me show you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.15,0:36:46.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你說的對\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.82,0:36:48.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,袖扣還是有點好處的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}These cufflinks are good for something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.92,0:36:52.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這招真炫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Neat trick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.19,0:36:54.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人，萊諾？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who are you really, Lionel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:57.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,相關第三方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A concerned third party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.17,0:37:02.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在怎麼辦？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.07,0:37:06.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我覺得你朋友說的中暑不是開玩笑的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I think your friend wasn't kidding about the heat stroke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們不可能從這衝出去\N{\reng_1 - 1080}There's no way we can bust out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:11.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>喂！</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.51,0:37:13.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:14.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>喂！</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.45,0:37:16.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,會有人聽見嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You think anyone can hear us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.06,0:37:26.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你在這幹嘛？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What are you doing here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.96,0:37:30.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我？你在這幹嘛？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Me? What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.23,0:37:32.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你不是扮警探去了嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I thought you were out playing detective.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.63,0:37:36.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我的重案線索指向我們的號碼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}My priority homicide traced back to our number.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.03,0:37:37.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那個賣假包的人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The guy selling knock-off handbags{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.94,0:37:40.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看見一個碼頭工殺了被害人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}saw a dock worker kill their victim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:43.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你接手的是麥洛·雅各布斯的案子？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That homicide you picked up was Milo Jacobs?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.58,0:37:45.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就是他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's our guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.58,0:37:47.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,法斯克呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Where's Fusco?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.08,0:37:51.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在這附近\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Here somewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:53.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大熊，<i>調查</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Bear, zoek.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.42,0:38:00.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,米奇和他手下還躲在某處\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mickey and his goons are still out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.23,0:38:02.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你去找法斯克和約會顧問\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You get Fusco and the pick-up artist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.29,0:38:04.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我去搜他們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm gonna go hunting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.06,0:38:05.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>喂！</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.26,0:38:06.46,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,法斯克？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fusco?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:07.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我們在這！</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're in here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.07,0:38:17.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你來了真好，搭檔\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nice of you to show up, partner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:19.14,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我就要結束今天的第三個案子了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I was about to close my third case of the day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.14,0:38:20.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,得確保你不會沒等我\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Wanted to make sure you didn't die{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.58,0:38:22.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有機會吹牛就先死了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}before I had a chance to brag about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.25,0:38:24.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,米奇還沒落網，我要抓住他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mickey's still out there. I'm gonna get him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.93,0:38:46.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,從來都不給夠子彈\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They never give you enough ammo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.06,0:39:11.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,小心，萊諾！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Look out, Lionel!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.70,0:39:23.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>大熊, 安靜</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Bear, heel!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.98,0:39:28.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,多謝支援\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Thanks for the backup.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.41,0:39:29.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,隨時效勞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Anytime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.58,0:39:34.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,身手不錯，約會顧問\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nice moves, wingman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:37.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.16,0:39:44.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,幫個忙好嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hey, guys, give me a hand here, will you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.83,0:39:50.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.70,0:39:56.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這個漂亮的山寨包是你買的，萊利？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I have you to thank for this lovely knockoff, Riley?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.77,0:39:58.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,顏色不適合我\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It wasn't my color.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.61,0:40:03.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,聽說你之前的包裏都是煙味\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I heard your old one smelled like an ashtray.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.24,0:40:04.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這些又是什麼人？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who are these mooks?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.61,0:40:06.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,拉脫維亞團伙\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Latvian mob.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.75,0:40:08.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們接到匿名電話\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We got an anonymous phone call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.38,0:40:10.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在唐人街的廠房裏發現了他們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Found 'em in a Chinatown sweatshop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.18,0:40:12.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很奇怪的案子\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Very strange case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.12,0:40:14.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們都被打傷了膝蓋\N{\reng_1 - 1080}They were all shot in the knees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.39,0:40:15.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要不是事先知道\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If I didn't know any better,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.86,0:40:18.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我還以為是你幹的呢，萊利\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'd think it was your doing, Riley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.63,0:40:20.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,今天大家幹得不錯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Great work today, guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.59,0:40:23.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你真是力轉乾坤\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You really managed to turn things around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.10,0:40:25.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,多謝誇獎，隊長\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Thank you, Captain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.23,0:40:27.70,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,今晚我請客喝酒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Drinks on me tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.44,0:40:34.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我，呃…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.24,0:40:38.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看來你終於學會當好警察了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I guess you figured out how to be a good cop after all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.04,0:40:41.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,需要過程，萊諾\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's a process, Lionel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.11,0:40:44.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,今晚喝酒的事，我…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Listen, about those drinks tonight, I, uh--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.72,0:40:47.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我已經有約了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I got somewhere to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:49.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,庫珀衝破你的約會前線了？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Cooper came through on the dating front?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.50,0:40:58.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這邊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Right over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.46,0:41:03.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.07,0:41:04.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我馬上回來，好嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'll be back. Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.30,0:41:06.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.01,0:41:10.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一杯蘇打水，一杯夏敦埃，謝謝\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A club soda and a glass of chardonnay, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.84,0:41:12.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你把酒灑她身上了嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You spill your drink on her yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.45,0:41:17.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在某些文化裏這是求偶儀式\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's a mating ritual in some cultures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.82,0:41:22.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我要指證米奇和他同夥\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm testifying against Mickeynd his boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.82,0:41:25.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你說的對\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You were right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.19,0:41:26.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,無法逃脫過去\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You can't run from your past,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:29.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,起碼不挨槍子是逃不過的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}at least not without getting shot at, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.66,0:41:35.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,記住，要有眼神接觸，自信點\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Remember, eye contact, confidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.93,0:41:37.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要享受其中\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Make sure you're having fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.60,0:41:39.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,安德烈，我能搞定\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Andre, I got this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.27,0:41:42.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我知道你行\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I know you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.94,0:41:45.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不過如果你還需要複習課程\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But if you ever need a refresher course,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.61,0:41:47.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,記得打給我\N{\reng_1 - 1080}you give me a call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.11,0:41:49.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.45,0:41:54.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,給你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:57.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.19,0:41:59.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Welcome back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.32,0:42:05.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,拉脫維亞團伙不再需要這些物資了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our Latvian friends won't be needing these supplies anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.71,0:42:23.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這是機器計劃的？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This was the machine's plan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.38,0:42:29.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,它堅信要救你的無關號碼，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She believes in saving your irrelevant numbers, Harold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.89,0:42:32.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而在你無法獲取\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And while you can't access{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.19,0:42:34.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,以前的銀行賬戶期間…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}any of your old bank accounts right now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.56,0:42:39.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,情況也在好轉\N{\reng_1 - 1080}things are looking up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.27,0:42:51.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,機器能提供我們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The only way the machine{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.77,0:42:54.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這種資金支援的唯一方法\N{\reng_1 - 1080}could give us this kind of financial assistance{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.61,0:43:00.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就是以撒瑪利亞不會發現的方式\N{\reng_1 - 1080}was to do so in a way that Samaritan would never discover.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:04.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不義之財，善加利用\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ill-gotten gains put to good use.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.19,0:43:09.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許你該給再它一次機會了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Maybe it's time you give her a second chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.89,0:43:16.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那枚導彈怎麼辦？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What will we do with the missile?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.20,0:43:19.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我相信我們會有辦法的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm sure we'll think of something.{\r}
